6to4
  ifconfig stf0 create
  ifconfig stf0 inet6 $6to4 prefixlen 16 alias
  route add -inet6 default 2002:c058:6301::


6to4 public routers
6to4 operates over public internet infrastructure, the routers can be reached under the following anycast addresses:
IPv4: 192.88.99.1
IPv6: 2002:c058:6301::

Building a 6to4-prefix
The 6to4 clientâ€™s own prefix is created from the 6to4 2002::/16 prefix with the following method (WWXX:YYZZ is the hexadecimal representation of the public IPv4 address w.x.y.z):
2002:WWXX:YYZZ::/48
